25
00:01:09,780 --> 00:01:10,780
A dream that's real

26
00:01:19,780 --> 00:01:20,780
Miss MU

27
00:01:21,780 --> 00:01:22,780
I'm Jingjing, I'm such a big fan of you!

28
00:01:25,780 --> 00:01:26,780
What are you doing?

29
00:01:26,780 --> 00:01:28,780
Sing me a song, please.

30
00:01:28,780 --> 00:01:31,780
Miss, I can't sing anymore.

31
00:01:32,780 --> 00:01:34,780
Ah, why?

32
00:01:34,780 --> 00:01:38,780
Because I've been poisoned by a very strange curse.

33
00:01:38,780 --> 00:01:41,780
Unless I untie the knot in my heart,

34
00:01:41,780 --> 00:01:44,780
I'll never wake up again,

35
00:01:44,780 --> 00:01:46,780
and never sing again.

36
00:01:47,780 --> 00:01:49,780
How do I untie your heart knot?

37
00:01:49,780 --> 00:01:51,780
I'll go ask my uncle for help.

38
00:01:51,780 --> 00:01:53,780
He's always drooling over your photo—

39
00:01:53,780 --> 00:01:55,780
he'll definitely help you!

40
00:01:56,780 --> 00:02:21,319
Hey, little girl, I don't even know you, yet you care so much about me. Maybe in this world, only you and Wen Kang truly care. Perhaps I really can't wake up. So I'll tell you the wrong I've done. Many years ago, I wasn't a big star yet.

41
00:02:26,780 --> 00:02:32,920
DO MI SO

42
00:02:32,920 --> 00:02:35,780
Xiaolu, Xiaolu

43
00:02:35,780 --> 00:02:41,120
Xiaolu, you know? Tuna Town's

44
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:43,000
star variety show,

45
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:45,039
Smile Match, is holding a talent contest.

46
00:02:45,039 --> 00:02:47,780
Let's go together!

47
00:02:47,780 --> 00:02:51,360
I... I don't want to go.

48
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:53,900
You go instead.

49
00:02:53,900 --> 00:02:56,199
You're pretty and sing well—

50
00:02:56,200 --> 00:02:58,520
you'll definitely win the championship.

51
00:02:58,520 --> 00:03:02,600
You're always so slow

52
00:03:02,600 --> 00:03:03,500
Just like a clover's nature

53
00:03:03,500 --> 00:03:04,300
You never change

54
00:03:04,300 --> 00:03:05,620
We've studied music for so long

55
00:03:05,620 --> 00:03:06,680
Isn't it so more people

56
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:08,040
Can hear our work?

57
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:09,460
What's wrong with you?

58
00:03:09,460 --> 00:03:11,080
This is such a great chance

59
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:12,600
Once we become champions

60
00:03:12,600 --> 00:03:14,500
We'll be huge stars

61
00:03:14,500 --> 00:03:16,700
Weren't you always trying

62
00:03:16,700 --> 00:03:18,220
To lighten your brother's load?

63
00:03:18,220 --> 00:03:24,420
Let's go together

64
00:03:24,420 --> 00:03:27,420
Um... alright then

65
00:03:34,420 --> 00:03:36,420
The elimination rounds are down to this

66
00:03:36,420 --> 00:03:38,420
We have only two contestants left

67
00:03:38,420 --> 00:03:41,420
Competing for the championship throne

68
00:03:45,420 --> 00:03:46,420
That's right

69
00:03:46,420 --> 00:03:48,420
They are the lively and cheerful

70
00:03:48,420 --> 00:03:50,420
Sweet-voiced Miss MU

71
00:03:50,420 --> 00:03:53,940
And the gentle, multi-talented Xiao Lu

72
00:03:53,940 --> 00:03:57,200
One week from now

73
00:03:57,200 --> 00:03:59,300
Our two contestants will perform

74
00:03:59,300 --> 00:04:00,840
Their own original songs

75
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:02,940
In the final showdown

76
00:04:02,940 --> 00:04:13,620
The championship trophy—who will take it home in the end?

77
00:04:13,620 --> 00:04:19,840
Let's wait and see.

78
00:04:20,420 --> 00:04:24,180
What do we do? What do we do?

79
00:04:24,180 --> 00:04:25,819
Only one week left.

80
00:04:25,819 --> 00:04:28,379
But I just can't pick a good song.

81
00:04:28,379 --> 00:04:30,439
Miss MU, are you there?

82
00:04:30,439 --> 00:04:31,660
I'm Xiaolu.

83
00:04:31,660 --> 00:04:35,259
I'll be right there.

84
00:04:35,259 --> 00:04:39,759
Miss MU

85
00:04:39,759 --> 00:04:42,580
I just wrote a song for my brother's birthday.

86
00:04:42,580 --> 00:04:44,480
I'll show it to you first.

87
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:47,520
From now on, you can't call me slowpoke anymore!

88
00:04:47,520 --> 00:04:48,800
Let me take a look.

89
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:57,579
Awesome!

90
00:04:57,579 --> 00:05:01,300
Xiaolu, you're amazing!

91
00:05:01,300 --> 00:05:01,900
Yeah.

92
00:05:01,900 --> 00:05:05,879
I'll sing this song in the finals.

93
00:05:05,879 --> 00:05:08,080
It's a bit tight on time.

94
00:05:08,080 --> 00:05:11,160
Perfect as a birthday gift for big bro!

95
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:14,180
Oh, haha, nice!

96
00:05:14,180 --> 00:05:16,900
I bet your brother will be thrilled.

97
00:05:16,900 --> 00:05:17,460
Just that

98
00:05:17,459 --> 00:05:21,139
I think there are a few minor flaws.

99
00:05:21,139 --> 00:05:24,019
No worries though.

100
00:05:24,019 --> 00:05:25,719
Let me take another look.

101
00:05:25,719 --> 00:05:29,579
Can you pour me a glass of water?

102
00:05:29,579 --> 00:05:31,099
Sure.

103
00:05:31,099 --> 00:05:32,620
I'll go get it right away.

104
00:05:47,459 --> 00:05:51,459
Xiaolu.

105
00:05:51,459 --> 00:05:52,459
Sorry.

106
00:05:52,459 --> 00:05:54,459
I didn't mean to.

107
00:05:54,459 --> 00:05:56,459
I...

108
00:05:56,459 --> 00:05:57,459
I...

109
00:05:57,459 --> 00:05:58,459
It's okay.

110
00:05:58,459 --> 00:05:59,459
It's not your fault.

111
00:05:59,459 --> 00:06:02,459
I'll just rewrite another copy.

112
00:06:03,459 --> 00:06:04,459
Sorry.

113
00:06:04,459 --> 00:06:06,459
It's all my fault.

114
00:06:06,459 --> 00:06:18,539
Now let's invite Miss MU to sing her original song.

115
00:06:18,539 --> 00:06:21,759
Her song is...

116
00:06:21,759 --> 00:06:24,419
Happy Birthday.

117
00:06:24,419 --> 00:06:32,039
Happy birthday to you.

118
00:06:32,039 --> 00:06:35,659
Happy birthday to you.

119
00:06:35,659 --> 00:06:36,439
Happy birthday to you.

120
00:06:36,439 --> 00:06:38,600
No way, I don't know.

121
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:40,980
Miss MU wouldn't do this.

122
00:06:40,980 --> 00:06:42,060
I'm dreaming.

123
00:06:42,060 --> 00:06:44,600
I must be dreaming.

124
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,899
Sis.

125
00:06:45,899 --> 00:06:47,000
What's wrong with you?

126
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:49,040
That's my song!

127
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:52,339
It was a birthday gift for you, big brother.

128
00:06:52,339 --> 00:06:54,659
Miss MU sang my song.

129
00:06:54,659 --> 00:06:55,899
What do I do?

130
00:06:55,899 --> 00:06:57,319
What do I do?

131
00:06:57,319 --> 00:06:59,540
She's my best friend.

132
00:07:14,319 --> 00:07:15,540
Thank you.

133
00:07:23,540 --> 00:07:25,259
I really regret it now.

134
00:07:28,259 --> 00:07:28,780
If only

135
00:07:28,780 --> 00:07:30,420
I could start over,

136
00:07:30,420 --> 00:07:35,100
I would treasure my friendship with Xiaolu.

137
00:07:35,100 --> 00:07:37,700
Xiaolu...

138
00:07:37,700 --> 00:07:40,760
I truly, truly regret it.

139
00:07:40,760 --> 00:07:44,580
Don't worry, Miss MU.

140
00:07:44,580 --> 00:07:46,760
Jingjing makes mistakes too,

141
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:47,900
and gets scolded by Locky Qi.

142
00:07:47,900 --> 00:07:50,740
You already know you did wrong.

143
00:07:50,740 --> 00:07:52,740
Xiaolu will forgive you.

144
00:07:58,780 --> 00:08:04,720
Wake up! Wake up! Wake up! Wake up! Wake up!

145
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:06,460
So lazy, still sleeping!

146
00:08:06,460 --> 00:08:08,020
You're supposed to be watching a patient,

147
00:08:08,020 --> 00:08:09,760
but you sleep more than anyone.

148
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:10,660
Get up!

149
00:08:10,660 --> 00:08:12,820
Xiaolu will forgive you.

150
00:08:12,820 --> 00:08:13,740
Xiaolu...

151
00:08:13,740 --> 00:08:18,100
Who is Xiaolu?

152
00:08:18,100 --> 00:08:21,220
Looks like Miss MU's condition hasn't improved.

153
00:08:21,220 --> 00:08:24,120
I'll come back later to check on her.

154
00:08:28,780 --> 00:08:35,700
Any progress?

155
00:08:35,700 --> 00:08:38,680
After investigation,

156
00:08:38,680 --> 00:08:41,340
the two girls who presented flowers during the performance

157
00:08:41,340 --> 00:08:43,779
had paint on their faces

158
00:08:43,779 --> 00:08:46,580
because they just came from a friend's birthday party

159
00:08:46,580 --> 00:08:48,080
and hadn't washed it off yet

160
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:50,100
before attending Miss MU's concert.

161
00:08:50,100 --> 00:08:55,259
As for the man in the mask,

162
00:08:55,259 --> 00:08:57,560
he had a severe cold

163
00:08:57,560 --> 00:08:59,460
but really liked Miss MU,

164
00:08:59,460 --> 00:09:01,800
so he attended the concert despite being sick.

165
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:05,280
None of them could be suspects.

166
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:09,340
Maybe we should change our angle

167
00:09:09,340 --> 00:09:11,480
and start considering people close to Miss MU.

168
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:16,220
This one's not it, that one's not it either.

169
00:09:16,220 --> 00:09:19,380
Who is the real culprit?

170
00:09:19,380 --> 00:09:19,780
Uncle,

171
00:09:19,780 --> 00:09:22,880
I think that Song Wen Kang from earlier is suspicious.

172
00:09:22,879 --> 00:09:27,620
He has no relation to Miss MU,

173
00:09:27,620 --> 00:09:29,500
yet he came to visit her in the middle of the night—

174
00:09:29,500 --> 00:09:31,100
that's already suspicious enough.

175
00:09:31,100 --> 00:09:32,240
Plus, just now—

176
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:34,799
He suddenly left the ward in a hurry.

177
00:09:34,799 --> 00:09:37,080
I'll come back to visit later then.

178
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:40,419
All of this is highly suspicious.

179
00:09:40,419 --> 00:09:44,240
Locky Qi makes a good point.

180
00:09:44,240 --> 00:09:46,539
Why don't we go together now

181
00:09:46,539 --> 00:09:48,019
and investigate this person.

182
00:09:52,879 --> 00:10:22,860
【ED Ending Theme】

183
00:10:22,879 --> 00:10:27,879
Tomorrow waves to me on the horizon.

184
00:10:27,879 --> 00:10:31,500
Every day in sunrise and sunset,

185
00:10:31,500 --> 00:10:35,500
turning into time, dreaming more.

186
00:10:35,500 --> 00:10:40,960
Expecting every second, every moment in life.

187
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:47,259
Bright eyes are sparkling,

188
00:10:47,259 --> 00:10:50,600
facing the sun with a smile.

189
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:55,840
It's not sneaky, just at the corner ahead.